该大学共开设超过200个本科、研究生及职业教育专业。以其建筑、农业（特别是动物科学和家禽学）、<ref name="meatpoultry.com_link">{{cite web | title=Meat and Poultry Magazine College Rankings | url=http://www.meatpoultry.com/articlearchives/archive_article.asp?ArticleID=72713 | accessdate=November 1, 2004 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050309021215/http://www.meatpoultry.com/articlearchives/archive_article.asp?ArticleID=72713 | archivedate=2005-03-09}} </ref>商科、历史、法律、中东研究等专业而知名。<ref name="dailyheadlines.uark.edu/5292.htm">{{cite web | title=University of Arkansas – Daily Headlines | url=http://dailyheadlines.uark.edu/5292.htm | accessdate=September 13, 2005 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051231083410/http://dailyheadlines.uark.edu/5292.htm | archivedate=2005-12-31| deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>"Colleges" {{cite web |url=http://www.uark.edu/home/11009.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-05-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531081947/http://www.uark.edu/home/11009.php |archivedate=2010-05-31 }} Retrieved on May 20, 2010.</ref>

它是美国排名靠前的公立大學之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/fayetteville-ar/university-of-arkansas-1108 |title=University of Arkansas – Best College – Education – US News |publisher=Colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com |date=August 17, 2010 |accessdate=January 24, 2011 |archive-date=2011-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110105114909/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/fayetteville-ar/university-of-arkansas-1108 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，其萨姆·M·沃尔顿商学院在全美公立商学院中排在前40位，整体则在前60位<ref>{{cite web|last=College |first=Walton |url=http://sammwaltoncollegeofbusiness.blogspot.com/2009/08/walton-college-ranks-24th-in-us-news.html |title=Sam M. Walton College of Business: Walton College Ranks 24th in U.S. News for Third Year |publisher=Sammwaltoncollegeofbusiness.blogspot.com |date=August 24, 2009 |accessdate=January 24, 2011}}</ref>。2011年，其费伊·琼斯建筑学院（Fay Jones School of Architecture）的本科教育在全美建筑学院中排前30<ref>{{cite web |url=http://architecture.uark.edu/548.php |title=School of Architecture Ranked 20th in Nation and Included in List of World-Class Schools | University of Arkansas Fay Jones School of Architecture |publisher=Architecture.uark.edu |date= |accessdate=January 24, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811172808/http://architecture.uark.edu/548.php |archivedate=2011年8月11日 |df= }}</ref>，法学院则在全美前150名内<ref>{{cite web|url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/items/03005 |title=University of Arkansas-Fayetteville – Best Law Schools – Graduate Schools – Education – US News |publisher=Grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com |date=April 15, 2010 |accessdate=January 24, 2011}}</ref>。

